IRM 1.4.17, Compliance Managers in Organization, Finance and Management, Resource Guide for Managers, dated March 1, 2006, is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal and the simultaneous publishing of IRM 1.4.29, Resource Guide for Managers, SB/SE Campus Exam/AUR, and W&I Exam Operations.
